## For more information, see Testing in Ktor Server

(https://ktor.io/docs/server-testing.html).

## TestApplication module loading

TestApplication no longer automatically loads modules from a configuration file ( e.g. application.conf). Instead, you must [explicitly load your modules](https://ktor.io/docs/migrating-3.html#explicit-module-loading) within the testApplication function or [load the configuration file](https://ktor.io/docs/migrating-3.html#configure-env) manually.

## Explicit module loading

To explicitly load modules, use the application function within testApplication. This approach allows you to manually specify which modules to load, providing greater control over your test setup.

